arChildNodes.szComment: FADE IN to LORATH kneeling beside a prone NEYRELLE.
LORATH takes a moment to examine her wounds. He is shocked/dismayed at how quickly the necrosis is spreading.
LORATH quickly begins to gather tinder.

LORATH places the head of his halberd upon the tinder.
He utters a brief incantation as the tinder ignites.
LORATH angrily glances off in the direction of her injuring event and then back to Neyrelle.
LORATH moves to NEYRELLE and tourniquets her arm.

The HERO crosses and kneels beside NEYRELLE.
Once the HERO has her, LORATH crosses and snatches up his HALBERD from the fire.
He turns to look at NEYRELLE, who is watching him, only barely conscious.
LORATH takes a deep breath as he crosses to NEYRELLE and takes his position over her.
With one deft motion, LORATH cleanly severs NEYRELLE’s arm at the elbow.

LORATH tosses his halberd aside, grabs up the infected limb and tosses it into the fire.
He then kneels beside NEYRELLE and begins bandaging the wound as she passes out.
After Neyrelle has fully passed out
